{"tid":1251586,"cid":18,"subCid":0,"title":"(多data)港警力列全球五強亞洲第一 但犯罪率跌全球最低 但警察人數預算破200億 你話對付邊個？？","createTime":"2019-06-22T14:57:45.000Z","updateTime":"2019-06-23T08:13:27.000Z","uid":221265,"like":57,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":11,"replies":[{"pid":"b7ea5b4a59790fb2d4756d10eee2dacb8769de87","tid":1251586,"uid":221265,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-22T14:57:45.000Z","msg":"<strong>先睇依個圖</strong><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/VbDn0WZ.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FVbDn0WZ.jpg&h=6f392bde&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/cUkJLoG.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FcUkJLoG.jpg&h=f884718a&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n6年前， <strong>聯合國毒品和犯罪問題辦公室</strong>統計，<strong>本港每10萬人口有約450名警察，警民比例在全球主要國家及地區中屬第五高，在亞洲區更屬最高，比例較新加坡多近兩倍。</strong><br />\n喺香港前後嘅國家，你睇下係邊類國家？一定唔係啲自由民主大國。 <br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.news.appledaily.com/local/daily/article/20131018/18469240\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2Fdaily%2Farticle%2F20131018%2F18469240&d=ahpQ5aMQEo4h8Mt%2B3j6t3gaB4GmEhO8grhZepf4200Y%3D&h=24daf596\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2Fdaily%2Farticle%2F20131018%2F18469240&h=b290658e\" target=\"_blank\">https://hk.news.appledaily.com/local/daily/article/20131018/18469240</a><br />\n睇埋6年前嘅報導，當年嘅警隊預算係140億。 <br />\n<br />\n<strong>再睇政府新聞處今年3月嘅稿</strong><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/3ioCPQD.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F3ioCPQD.jpg&h=6fe996fc&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n保安局局長李家超表示，本港罪案數字持續下跌，去年共錄得54,225宗，較2017年下跌3.2%，暴力罪案也下跌2.2%。<br />\n<br />\n李家超今日出席撲滅罪行委員會會議後會見傳媒。他指，最大跌幅的罪行為店鋪盜竊和縱火，兩者均下跌18%；爆竊案跌16%，嚴重毒品罪行和行劫均下跌約一成。<br />\n<br />\n香港嘅罪案其實係全球最低之一，要咁多警察做乜？<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/CPAd7FA.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FCPAd7FA.jpg&h=e8b76e19&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<strong>再睇埋立場同城寨做嘅圖：</strong><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/42yCPQ8.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F42yCPQ8.jpg&h=fcbd782d&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/mUs8b4t.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FmUs8b4t.jpg&h=3594ec6c&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/6VJLehP.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F6VJLehP.jpg&h=2c909881&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n短短6年，警隊預算由<span style=\"color: red;\">140億暴增到207億，多咗47%</span>！我諗如果聯合國依家再做全球警力調查，香港入top 3不是夢！<br />\n尋晚蘋果話有5000警力喺警總附近，一有人衝就出嚟鎮壓。 你話一年警務處一年207億1年加成千警察，加晒喺EU/PTU。 依家香港變咗police state，亦係林鄭點解唔敢成立<strong><span style=\"color: red;\">獨立調查委員會</span></strong>，因為佢要靠警察鐵腕rule香港。 <br />\n<br />\n大家依家唔好空喊口號，要努力了解香港體制嘅details，努力了解下制度有幾暴力。"},{"pid":"6a416acd5b22a402dc7996afd8776dfe2c06fbfc","tid":1251586,"uid":88123,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-22T14:58:41.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ef5c8bbda9a5ec7f0bfbb2c7db957e13ae4d5d51","tid":1251586,"uid":221265,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-22T15:02:13.000Z","msg":"push"},{"pid":"60290be17c0a721e6d1047f89c690a5478dd189f","tid":1251586,"uid":67118,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-06-22T15:04:49.000Z","msg":"維穩費咁年年加<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />  <br />\n再加落去整隊軍隊都夠"},{"pid":"76b3a2490b454c3cb64a6eeac9d0fee9ae7dc85d","tid":1251586,"uid":71071,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-06-22T15:09:54.000Z","msg":"返工去力威，得閒就屌鴒鳩巿民，學歷要求低，智歷更加冇要求，警犬<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"88d4d8644fbbd18f9cc1c40fde94df3582c52821","tid":1251586,"uid":71071,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"76b3a2490b454c3cb64a6eeac9d0fee9ae7dc85d","tid":1251586,"uid":71071,"li